<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c4">[عَهْ]</span>: صِيَاحٌ بالغنم.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>و <span class="c4">[عَوْ]</span>: زَجْرٌ للمعز.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>... فُعْلٌ، بضم الفاء<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
